Introduction
============
This is a basic Reddit/Hacker News/Digg clone. Users can submit links, vote them up (no downvoting), and comment on them.

Setup
=====

To create the admin user and the three roles, please run `rake db:seed`

This will create the following three roles:
- user
- moderator
- admin


Role Descriptions
=================

The user role grants people basic access to the site. This role is granted to people who sign up by themselves.
The moderator role grants people ability to edit links and comments submitted by other people.
The admin role can edit other links, delete links, and create new users and grant them any role. They can also edit and delete others' comments.